OL,3,C'It's unacceptable': Residents a week
OL,4,Cinto water supply issues
OL,6,FAreas in Cornwall are a week into
OL,7,Fwater supply problems.
OL,9,FThe supply problems have been
OL,10,Faffecting postcode areas TR8 to PL27 -
OL,11,Fan 11 mile stretch including Newquay,
OL,12,FPolzeth, Wadebridge and St Eval near
OL,13,FPadstow.
OL,15,FSouth West Water has sent tankers to
OL,16,Fthe area to boost supplies and have
OL,17,Fnow confirmed they will be paying
OL,18,Fcompensation to people affected.
