OL,3,C'It's unacceptable': Residents a week
OL,4,Cinto water supply issues
OL,6,FHouseholds are being given #50
OL,7,Fcompensation, while businesses, who
OL,8,Fsay they've lost as much as #45,000
OL,9,Fhave been offered #100.
OL,11,FLocal MP Ben Maguire has been in
OL,12,Fregular contact with South West Water.
OL,13,FHe's highly critical of the way the
OL,14,Fcompany has handled the issue.
OL,16,FHe said: "I am today calling for Susan
OL,17,FDavy, the chief executive, to
OL,18,Fseriously consider her position
OL,19,Fbecause she's paid #860,000 a year and
OL,20,Fwe get this awful service.
