OL,3,C'It's unacceptable': Residents a week
OL,4,Cinto water supply issues
OL,6,F"I'd like to say to her directly, she
OL,7,Fneeds to start acting her wage. Come
OL,8,Fhere to St Eval and meet with me and
OL,9,Fthe residents here to understand the
OL,10,Fhuge frustration that we have.
OL,12,F"It's unacceptable that people are
OL,13,Fpaying huge water rates and yet
OL,14,Fthey're receiving this dire service."
OL,16,FAt the Carnewas Tea Room staff had to
OL,17,Fclose early nearly every day this week
OL,18,Fbecause their taps run dry in the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
