OL,3,C'It's unacceptable': Residents a week
OL,4,Cinto water supply issues
OL,6,FOwner Craig Archer said: "We work
OL,7,Freally hard. It's the start of the
OL,8,Fseason. We all build up to this and
OL,9,Fthen we get knocked down."
OL,11,FLocal resident Zoe Coe said: "You just
OL,12,Fhave to fill up bottles and hope that
OL,13,Fyou're going to have enough water
OL,14,Fthrough the day. And it's been really
OL,15,Fhot as well. So it's not been very
OL,16,Fhelpful."
OL,18,FAt the Traveller's Rest pub they had
OL,19,Fto shut for three days - food had to
OL,20,Fbe thrown out and it's cost them
OL,21,F#45,000.
