OL,3,C'It's unacceptable': Residents a week
OL,4,Cinto water supply issues
OL,6,FHead Chef Paul Snow said: "It's a hard
OL,7,Fenough time as it is anyway, running
OL,8,Fpubs and hospitality businesses. We've
OL,9,Fsuffered at the beginning of school
OL,10,Fholidays where we've got thousands and
OL,11,Fthousands of people coming down. It's
OL,12,Fjust crazy."
OL,14,FOver the last few months ITV News West
OL,15,FCountry has repeatedly asked to speak
OL,16,Fto South West Water CEO Susan Davey.
OL,18,FOn Friday 2 August, the company's
OL,19,Fdrinking water director defended the
OL,20,Fcompany's actions.
