OL,3,C'It's unacceptable': Residents a week
OL,4,Cinto water supply issues
OL,6,FRichard Stanbrook said: "We are
OL,7,Fproactively talking to our customers,
OL,8,Fmaking sure that they do report to us
OL,9,Fif they are experiencing issues and we
OL,10,Fare in the field checking on those
OL,11,Fcustomers.
OL,13,F"As soon as we understood the problem
OL,14,Fthat was arising for a number of our
OL,15,Fcustomers, we put tankers in to
OL,16,Fmaintain the pressure. Our sincere
OL,17,Fapologies to those customers that were
OL,18,Faffected."
